title: 8 Ways We Waste Money and 8 Ways to Manage it Better
description: This week, we're talking money.Do you feel you manage your money well or is there room for improvement? Whether it's skipping the Starbucks in the morning or learning how to invest, there are many ways to go about it.Listen to my 8 practical tips to help you save money and all the habits you can implement in order to improve your relationship with money.
author: onpurposepodcast@jayshetty.me (Jay Shetty)
